official_title: A bill relating to the Tiwa Indian Pueblo of San Juan de Guadalupe, Tortugas, N. Mexico.

summary.text: Designates the Indians now living in the pueblo of San Juan de Guadalupe, New Mexico, as the Tiwa Indians of San Juan de Guadalupe, Tortugas, New Mexico. Extends Federal recognition to such tribe.
